                    <div class="skills-icon p-2 rounded-circle">
                        <i class="fas fa-comments fa-fw"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h6 class="text-uppercase font-weight-bold my-3">Free Support</h6>
                    <div class="skills-underline"></div>
                    <p class="w-75 mx-auto text-muted">Our dedicated support team is always ready to assist you with any questions or concerns, providing you with free and reliable customer service.</p>
                </div>
